headline: Uber’s Robotaxi Push And Valuation Gap Put Future Growth In Focus
summary: Uber Technologies (NYSE:UBER) is ramping up its autonomous vehicle efforts with a large investment in Waabi and plans to deploy more than 25,000 robotaxis. The company has created Uber AV Labs to use its real world trip data to support autonomous driving development and integration on its platform. New collaborations with Mercedes Benz and Nvidia aim to build a global robotaxi platform across key markets. Uber Technologies, trading at around $80.05, is pushing further into autonomous...
